    <briefdescription>
<para>UHC endpoint buffer info. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This structure is mandatory for all UHC request. It contains the meta data about the request and FIFOs to store <ref refid="structnet__buf" kindref="compound">net_buf</ref> structures for each request.</para>
<para>The members of this structure should not be used directly by a higher layer (host stack). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
